                "data": {
                  "title": "Winrock International.",
                  "subtitle": "Global nonprofit leader in carbon market integrity and nature-based climate solutions. Winrock operates ACR, one of the world's first voluntary greenhouse gas registries, and pioneers science-based carbon crediting methodologies. Within the CCF, it ensures the rigor of carbon accounting and emissions verification standards."
